    dc:description "Fig. 29. Distribution map of Afrocyclus gen. nov. T indicates type localities. Provinces and major cities are labelled." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3517580/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3517588>
    dc:description "Fig. 33. Afrocyclus exsertus (Melvill & Ponsonby, 1903) gen. et comb. nov. A. Holotype (NHMUK 1904.4.29.28). B. Aperture view (ELM D16953). C. Protoconch (ELM D16951). D. Detail of axial lamellae of periostracum (ELM D16951). E. Dorsal view (ELM D16951). F. Ventral view (ELM W3654). G. Portion of radula (ELM W3654). H. Operculum (ELM W3654). I. Penis, dorsal view (ELM W3654). J. Operculum, lateral view (ELM W3655). K. Penis, lateral view (ELM W3654). Scale bars: A = 3 mm; B, E = 1 mm; C, H–K = 500 µm; D = 200 µm; F = 2 mm; G = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3517588/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3517590>
    dc:description "Fig. 34. A. Cyathopoma meredithae (Bruggen, 1983) comb. nov., paratype and close-up of operculum (NHMUK 198338). B. Cyathopoma chirindae (Bruggen, 1986) comb. nov. (NMSA L4904). Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3517590/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3517592>
    dc:description "Fig. 35. Cyathopoma pembense Rowson, 2010. A–D. ELM D18464. A, C. Operculum. B. Portion of radula. D. Penis, lateral view. Scale bars: A, C–D = 500 µm; B = 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3517592/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3517594>
    dc:description "Fig. 36. Cyclotus sp. A. Aperture view (NMSA L7108). B. Dorsal view (NMSA L7108). C–D. Operculum (NMSA L7108). E. Cyclotus variegatus Swainson, 1840 operculum (NHMUK1893.6.7.43-5). F. Portion of radula (NMSA L7108). G. Penis, dorsal view (NMSA L7108). H. Penis lateral view (NMSA L7108). Scale bars: A–B = 2 mm; C, E = 1 mm; D, G–H = 500 µm; F = 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3517594/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

